Demi Rose, 27, has taken to Instagram to show off her curves in a glittering new dress. The model pouted for the camera as she flaunted her assets in a short clip. She could be seen wearing a light blue and purple, scaled two-piece dress with a slit at the hip revealing her thigh. The star wore her brown hair long and straight as she posed for the camera. Demi also wore brown sandals and a golden handbag to match. She asked fans in the following post: “Did you miss my dark hair?”